- @title = 'Installation'
%h1 Installation

%p
  It requires
  %ul
    %li TokyoCabinet, a b-tree key/value disk store
    %li libevent, for asynchronous sockets and HTTP
    %li Yajl, for JSON generation

%h2 
  Mac OS X
  = link_to '#', '#macos', :class => 'page_place'
  
%p
  For compiling you should have installed xcode

%p 
  Run this in terminal
  
  %pre.code
    :preserve
      sudo port install yajl tokyocabinet libevent tokyocabinet libzip
      git clone http://github.com/stevedekorte/vertexdb.git
      cd vertexdb
      ./bin/compile
      

